<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1437,151,752]" pageId="7" pageNumber="299">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,382,620,645]" pageId="7" pageNumber="299">Natural history</emphasis>
. No precise details on the habits of this species are available. It was described from “ 
<collectingCountry box="[1352,1437,620,645]" name="Bolivia" pageId="7" pageNumber="299">Bolivia</collectingCountry>
(Tonampayo)” but this location was not found in any other reference.
</paragraph>
